to buy or to buy a stake
in a business very fast?

00:23:45.109 --> 00:23:48.010
LOIC DE KERDREL: Well, I'm
not sure it's very rational,

00:23:48.010 --> 00:23:48.560
I would say.

00:23:48.560 --> 00:23:53.150
There's a large part
of instinct that I

00:23:53.150 --> 00:23:59.670
feel through the exchange,
the talk with the founders.

00:23:59.670 --> 00:24:04.280
And I invest very early stage.

00:24:04.280 --> 00:24:07.070
So I would say knowing
the statistic is

00:24:07.070 --> 00:24:08.420
you invest in 10 companies.

00:24:08.420 --> 00:24:11.260
And one goes very well.

00:24:11.260 --> 00:24:13.554
And most of the others
died, basically.

