AUDIENCE: OK.

00:34:47.715 --> 00:34:48.739
LINO CATTARUZZI: No?

00:34:48.739 --> 00:34:50.864
If not, we're going to do
something very important.

00:34:50.864 --> 00:34:55.710
We're [INAUDIBLE] Loic to be
a mentor for Google as well.

